response.overview: On the one hand, there are five French engineers who recently set up IN'BÔ: the manufacture of bicycles, skateboards, eyewear and other wooden confections 100% made in France. Thanks to the strength of their group, they have developed a solid project based on an ecological manufacturing process to produce durable, high-tech products. We'd like to encourage their initiative and democratize the use of wooden sports equipment. With our experience of roaming in extreme environments, we'll be testing IN'BÔ's specially-built bikes in the Pamir mountains of Tajikistan to meet isolated communities.
response.title: Les œuvres du Pamir
